    <p>The list­ings on these Hap­pen­ings pages are free.</p>
    <p>Go to str.sg/hap­pen at least two weeks ahead. Re­quired in­for­ma­tion in­cludes the name of the event, or­gan­iser, venue, date and time, ticket prices and near­est MRT sta­tion, as well as your name, ad­dress and con­tact num­ber.</p>
